{"word":"G1497 - εἴδωλον - eídōlon - i'-do-lon - Idol","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἴδωλον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>eídōlon"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>i'-do-lon"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Idol"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"விக்கிரகம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"the image of a heathen god, a false god"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1491 - εἶδος - eîdos - i'-dos/1491\">G1491</a>; an <i>image</i> (that is, for worship); by implication a heathen <i>god</i>, or (plural) the <i>worship</i> of such: - idol."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1493 - εἰδωλεῖον - eidōleîon - i-do-li'-on/1493\">G1493</a>, <a href=\"#/G1494 - εἰδωλόθυτον - eidōlóthyton - i-do-loth'-oo-ton/1494\">G1494</a>, <a href=\"#/G1495 - εἰδωλολατρεία - eidōlolatreía - i-do-lol-at-ri'-ah/1495\">G1495</a>, <a href=\"#/G1496 - εἰδωλολάτρης - eidōlolátrēs - i-do-lol-at'-race/1496\">G1496</a>, <a href=\"#/G1497 - εἴδωλον - eídōlon - i'-do-lon/1497\">G1497</a>, <a href=\"#/G2712 - κατείδωλος - kateídōlos - kat-i'-do-los/2712\">G2712</a>"}]}